riend of mine who got lucky enough to have almost all the level 3 effects, he said the only ones that are actually worth ANYTHING are the ones that effect dot damage.  Mana conservation was so un-noticable, but the extra damage off dots was quite useful.</P><P><BR><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=107355" target="_blank">Those who have turned away, shall be turned upon. <br> Lich Ravanta Suffer</a>  <img src=icon_smile_evil.gif border=0 align=middle><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
